# CODEOWNERS - Defines individuals or teams responsible for code in this repository
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# These owners will be automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull request
# that modifies code that they own. 
#
# IMPORTANT: Order matters! More specific patterns should appear AFTER general patterns.
# The last matching pattern takes precedence.
#
# Teams must have explicit write access to the repository to be valid code owners.
# See TEAM_STRUCTURE.md for team definitions and permissions.

